import React from 'react';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  Container,
  Grid,
  Typography,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardMedia,
  Stack,
  Paper,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemIcon,
  ListItemText,
  Divider
} from '@mui/material';
import SearchIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Search';
import ChildCareIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ChildCare';
import TrackChangesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TrackChanges';
import FavoriteIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Favorite';
import CheckCircleOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CheckCircleOutline';
import SchoolIcon from '@mui/icons-material/School';
import PsychologyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Psychology';
import DirectionsRunIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DirectionsRun';
import RecordVoiceOverIcon from '@mui/icons-material/RecordVoiceOver';
import EmojiEmotionsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/EmojiEmotions';
import ColorLensIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ColorLens';

const HomePage = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box className="hero-section">
        <Container maxWidth="md">
          <Typography variant="h2" component="h1" gutterBottom>
            Educational Activities for Your Child's Development
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" paragraph>
            Find the perfect activities tailored to your child's age, interests, and developmental needs
          </Typography>
          <Stack direction={{ xs: 'column', sm: 'row' }} spacing={2} justifyContent="center" sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
            <Button 
              variant="contained" 
              size="large" 
              component={RouterLink} 
              to="/register"
              sx={{ px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
            >
              Get Started Free
            </Button>
            <Button 
              variant="outlined" 
              size="large" 
              color="inherit"
              component={RouterLink} 
              to="/about"
              sx={{ px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
            >
              Learn More
            </Button>
          </Stack>
        </Container>
      </Box>
      
      {/* Features Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 8 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h2" align="center" gutterBottom>
          Why Parents Love Our App
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="text.secondary" paragraph sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
          Designed by early childhood experts to make learning fun and hassle-free
        </Typography>
        
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/300x140/?children,play"
                alt="Smart search"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                  Smart Search Engine
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                  Find activities based on your child's age, interests, and the materials you already have at home.
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <SearchIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Filter by age, time, and materials" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <CheckCircleOutlineIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Find activities in seconds" />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/300x140/?child,development"
                alt="Personalized recommendations"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                  Personalized Recommendations
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                  Get activity suggestions tailored to your child's developmental needs and interests.
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <ChildCareIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Create profiles for each child" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <TrackChangesIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Target specific developmental areas" />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="140"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/300x140/?child,learning"
                alt="Progress tracking"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                  Progress Tracking
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                  Document your child's development and see how activities support specific milestones.
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <FavoriteIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Save favorite activities" />
                  </ListItem>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <CheckCircleOutlineIcon color="primary" />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText primary="Track completed activities" />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
      
      {/* Developmental Areas Section */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', py: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Typography variant="h3" component="h2" align="center" gutterBottom>
            Supporting All Areas of Development
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="text.secondary" paragraph sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
            Our activities are designed to nurture your child's growth across key developmental domains
          </Typography>
          
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <PsychologyIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Cognitive</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Problem-solving, critical thinking, memory, and concentration activities to develop your child's intellectual abilities.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <DirectionsRunIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Motor Skills</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Fine and gross motor activities to improve coordination, balance, and physical development.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <RecordVoiceOverIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Language</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Communication, vocabulary building, and early literacy activities to enhance language development.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <SchoolIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Social</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Activities that promote sharing, cooperation, and social interaction skills.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <EmojiEmotionsIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Emotional</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Help your child understand and express emotions through targeted activities.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <ColorLensIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5">Creativity</Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body1">
                  Art, music, and imaginative play activities to foster creative expression and innovation.
                </Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>
      
      {/* CTA Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="md" sx={{ py: 8, textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          Ready to Get Started?
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
          Join thousands of parents who are making learning fun and meaningful for their children.
        </Typography>
        <Button 
          variant="contained" 
          size="large" 
          component={RouterLink} 
          to="/register"
          sx={{ mt: 2, px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
        >
          Sign Up for Free
        </Button>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default HomePage;
